branchCategory.name: XLF, Aluminum High Vacuum Angle Valve, Normally Closed, O-ring Seal
branchCategory.description: <p>XLF is a normally closed, single acting high vacuum angle valve with an O-ring shaft seal.&nbsp; The XL* family shares common features with all series members.&nbsp; Bodies are made of aluminum for light weight and excellent thermal conductivity, resulting in a uniform temperature for the entire valve body.&nbsp; The body offers excellent resistance to fluorine corrosion.&nbsp; A low sputtering yield and the absence of heavy metals avoid wafer contamination.</p> <p>&nbsp;</p>
